Program: Outlook
Title: Aftermath of the Mumbai Bomb Attacks
Link: https://www.bbc.co.uk/programmes/p03kbsf3
Last Broadcast Date: Not available
How the people of Mumbai are regrouping after the bomb attacks two weeks ago. Also, New York's driving doctor whose car is his consulting room. The rise of Portuguese fado singer Dona Rosa from poor street musician to world wide aclaim. Finally Julia Fox Garrison talks about her stroke at the age of 37. Presenter: Frederick Dove. Show less